  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Shavendra was given the title of 'Mahamanya Pratapadhikesheva'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Chief of Defense Staff, General Shavendra Silva, has been awarded the honorary title of Mahamanya Pratapadhikeshevara by the Maha Sangha Sabha of the Asgiri faction.",
        "Today (28) in the afternoon, this honorary title was presented at the Asgiri Maha Vihara Abhinandana Festival held at the Asgiri Maha Vihara.",
        "The Asgiri Maha Sangha Sabha has decided to award this honorary title to Mr. General Shavendra Silva for his service to the country, religion and national security."
      ],
